<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540243>
    dc:description "Figures 215–224: Male postpachytenes (215, 217, 219), mitotic metaphases (216, 218), sister metaphases II (220), and ideograms (221–224) (y axis - % of the diploid chromosome length, dark grey marks chromosomes in multivalent association) of Reddyanus species from Southeast Asia. Figures 215, 221. R. furai sp. n. (2n=14, 7II). Figures 216, 222. R. majkusi sp. n. (2n=16). Figures 217, 223. R. rolciki sp. n. (2n=14, 7II). Figures 218–220, 224. R. schwotti sp. n. (2n=11, 1II+CIX). Arrows show chromosomes in multivalent association during postpachytene (219). Scale bar: 10 µm (215–220)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540243/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540239>
    dc:description "Figures 192–202: Reddyanus, males, pedipalp trochanter and femur, patella, and chela dorsal, metasoma II–III in lateral views. Figure 192. R. feti, holotype. Figure 193. R. furai sp. n., holotype. Figure 194. R. hofereki sp. n., holotype. Figure 195. R. jendeki, holotype. Figure 196. R. krasenskyi, Java, Ujung Kulon. Figure 197. R. majkusi sp. n., holotype. Figure 198. R. neradi, holotype. Figure 199. R. petrzelkai, holotype. Figure 200. R. rolciki sp. n., holotype. Figure 201. R. schwotti sp. n., Thailand, Khao sok. Figure 202. R. zideki, paratype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540239/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540241>
    dc:description "Figures 203–214: Reddyanus, males, telson lateral. Figure 203. R. feti, holotype. Figure 204. R. furai sp. n., holotype. Figure 205. R. hofereki sp. n., holotype. Figure 206. R. jendeki, holotype. Figure 207. R. krasenskyi, Java, Ujung Kulon. Figure 208. R. majkusi sp. n., holotype. Figure 209. R. neradi, holotype. Figure 210. R. petrzelkai, holotype. Figure 211. R. rolciki sp. n., holotype. Figure 212. R. schwotti sp. n., holotype. Figure 213. R. schwotti sp. n., paratype from Thailand, Khao sok. Figure 214. R. zideki, paratype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540241/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540247>
    dc:description "Figure 225. Map showing confirmed distribution of Reddyanus spp. in Southeast Asia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540247/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540194>
    dc:description "Figures 76–78. Reddyanus majkusi sp. n., male paratype in dorsal (76) and ventral (77) views. Metasoma V and telson lateral view. Scale bar: 10 mm (76–77)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540194/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540204>
    dc:description "Figures 111–112. Reddyanus majkusi sp. n., type locality." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540204/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540198>
    dc:description "Figures 90–108: Reddyanus majkusi sp. n. Figures 90–91, 103–105. Female paratype, pedipalp chela dorsal (90) and external (91) views, metasoma and telson in lateral (103), dorsal (104) and ventral (105) views. Figures 92–102, 106–108. Male holotype, pedipalp chela dorsal (92), external (93) and ventral (94) views, patella dorsal (95), external (96) and ventral (97) views, femur and trochanter internal (98), dorsal (99), and ventral (100) views, movable finger (101) and fixed finger (102) dentition, metasoma and telson in lateral (106), dorsal (107) and ventral (108) views. Trichobothrial pattern is indicated in Figures 93–96 and 98–99. Scale bar: 10 mm (103–108)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540198/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540202>
    dc:description "Figures 109–110. Reddyanus majkusi sp. n., male holotype (109) and female paratype (110) in vivo habitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540202/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540196>
    dc:description "Figures 79–89: Reddyanus majkusi sp. n. Figures 79, 81, 83–84, 86–89. Male holotype, carapace and tergites I–III (79), coxosternal area and sternite III (81), sternites V–VII (83), telson lateral (84), and left legs I–IV, retrolateral aspect (86–89). Figures 80, 82, 85. Female paratype, carapace and tergites I–III (80), coxosternal area and sternite III (82), and telson lateral (85) view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540196/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540214>
    dc:description "Figure 140. Reddyanus rolciki sp. n., male holotype in vivo habitus and its maturity exuvia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540214/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540212>
    dc:description "Figures 124–139: Reddyanus rolciki sp. n., male holotype, pedipalp chela dorsal (124), external (125) and ventral (126) views, patella dorsal (127), external (128) and ventral (129) views, femur and trochanter internal (130), dorsal (131), and ventral (132) views, movable finger (133) and fixed finger (134) dentition, metasoma and telson in lateral (135), dorsal (136) and ventral (137) views, and right legs III–IV, dorsal aspect (138–139). Trichobothrial pattern is indicated in Figures 125–128 and 130–131. Scale bar: 10 mm (135–137)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540212/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540210>
    dc:description "Figures 117–123: Reddyanus rolciki sp. n. Figure 117. Male paratype, carapace and tergites I–III. Figures 118–123. Male holotype, carapace and tergites I–III (118), coxosternal area and sternites III–V (119), and right legs I–IV, retrolateral aspect (120–123)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540210/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540216>
    dc:description "Figures 141–144: Reddyanus schwotti sp. n. Figures 141–142. Male holotype in dorsal (141) and ventral (142) views. Figures 143–144. Female paratype from type locality in dorsal (143) and ventral (144) views. Scale bars: 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540216/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540230>
    dc:description "Figures 187–188. Reddyanus schwotti sp. n., male holotype (187) and female paratype from type locality (188) in vivo habitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540230/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540226>
    dc:description "Figures 155–171: Reddyanus schwotti sp. n. Figures 155–156. Female paratype from Thailand Khao sok, pedipalp chela dorsal (155) and external (156) views. Figures 157–165. Male paratype from Cambodia, Kampot Province, Bokor, pedipalp chela dorsal (157), external (158) and ventral (159) views, patella dorsal (160), external (161) and ventral (162) views, femur and trochanter internal (163) and dorsal (164) views, movable finger dentition (165). Trichobothrial pattern is indicated in Figures 158–161 and 163–164. Figures 166–169. Male paratype from Thailand Khao sok, left legs I–IV, retrolateral aspect. Figures 170–171. Male paratype from Thailand, Tao Island, right legs III–IV, dorsal aspect." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540226/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540224>
    dc:description "Figures 147–154: Reddyanus schwotti sp. n. Figure 147. Male paratype from Thailand, Tao Island, carapace and tergites I–III. Figures 148, 151, 153. Male paratype from Thailand Khao sok, carapace and tergites I–II (148), coxosternal area and sternites III–IV (151), and telson lateral (153). Figures 149, 152, 154. Female paratype from Thailand Khao sok, carapace and tergites I–II (149), coxosternal area and sternites III–V (152), and telson lateral (154). Figure 150. Male paratype from Cambodia, Kampot Province, Bokor, carapace and tergites I–III." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540224/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540228>
    dc:description "Figures 172–186: Reddyanus schwotti sp. n., metasoma and telson in lateral (172, 175, 178, 181, 184), dorsal (173, 176, 179, 182, 185) and ventral (174, 177, 180, 183, 186) views. Figures 172–177. Female (172–174) and male (175–177) paratypes from Thailand Khao sok. Figures 178–180. Male paratype from Cambodia, Bokor. Figures 181–183. Male paratype from Thailand, Tao Island. Figures 184–186. Male holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540228/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6540237>
    dc:description "Figure 191. Reddyanus schwotti sp. n., male paratype from Cambodia, Kampot Province, Bokor in vivo habitus and its maturity exuvia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6540237/files/figure.png" ;
